                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Conger</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Petropolis</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-08-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 30,
                            1893</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Conger announces that the interdiction of cipher messages to Santos has
                        been removed.</p>
